title: Day 4 - Gates
itunes:title: Day 4 - Gates
itunes:subtitle: The Bad Days
description:
The Bad Days, Day 4: Around the world are holes...but not just any holes. Holes that have been reported to contain certain mystic and supernatural properties. Holes that supposedly have no bottom. Holes that defy explanation and have a connection to a horrible moment in history...
